{{Top|canon=Project Shantipole}}
{{Citation}}
The '''Shantipole Project''' was a venture devised by [[Commander/Legends|Commander]] [[Gial Ackbar/Legends|Gial Ackbar]] and the [[Verpine/Legends|Verpine]] colonies of [[Slayn & Korpil/Legends|Slayn & Korpil]] to create more effective [[Starfighter/Legends|starfighters]] for the [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Alliance to Restore the Republic]] during the [[Galactic Civil War/Legends|Galactic Civil War]].

The Shantipole Project was based at [[Research Station Shantipole]], an asteroid located in the [[Roche asteroid field|Roche asteroid belt]]. The [[A/SF-01 B-wing starfighter/Legends|B-wing starfighter]] was the major output of this project, and development of the [[B-wing/E starfighter]] (known as the "B-wing Expanded") soon followed. However, the Shantipole research facility was compromised by an [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] spy, who led [[Captain/Legends|Captain]] [[Kolaff]] to the Roche asteroids; the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] [[Corvette/Legends|corvette]], ''[[Javelin 3]]'' was one [[Starship/Legends|starship]] that was sent to [[Battle of Roche (Galactic Civil War)|destroy]] the project. [[Transport/Legends|Transports]] such as [[Shantipole (CR90 corvette)|''Shantipole'']] were able to evacuate personnel from the facility, though ultimately Ackbar's forces were able to drive Kolaff away. The [[Light freighter/Legends|light freighter]] ''[[Out Runner]]'' participated in the project.

